{"id":24143,"date":"2019-12-15T19:45:08","date_gmt":"2019-12-15T12:45:08","guid":{"rendered":"\/docs\/shortpixel\/lam-sao-su-dung-dinh-dang-webp"},"modified":"2019-12-16T11:12:36","modified_gmt":"2019-12-16T04:12:36","slug":"lam-sao-su-dung-dinh-dang-webp","status":"publish","type":"docs","link":"\/docs\/shortpixel\/lam-sao-su-dung-dinh-dang-webp","title":{"rendered":"C\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng \u1ea3nh WebP cho website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n?"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Shortpixel t\u1ea1o t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1o th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng \u1ea3nh WebP thumbnail <strong>&#8220;mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed&#8221;<\/strong> cho \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng WebP n\u1ebfu server b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 (do b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u00fa \u00dd: \u0110\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng \u1ea3nh WebP t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1edfi tr\u00ecnh duy\u1ec7t <strong>Safari<\/strong> c\u1ee7a &#8220;tr\u00e1i t\u00e1o&#8221; Apple tr\u00ean m\u00e1y t\u00ednh Mac hay Iphone, Ipad. B\u1ea1n tham kh\u1ea3o ngu\u1ed3n b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/WebP-support.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"535\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/WebP-support-1024x535.png\" alt=\"Webp Support\" class=\"wp-image-24181\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/WebP-support-1024x535.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/WebP-support-218x114.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/WebP-support-300x157.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/WebP-support-700x366.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/WebP-support-768x401.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/WebP-support.png 1586w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>WebP hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c tr\u00ecnh duy\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean (Ngu\u1ed3n: <a href=\"https:\/\/caniuse.com\/#feat=webp\">https:\/\/caniuse.com<\/a>)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch sau \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 &#8220;k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t&#8221; s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng webP:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>D\u00f9ng cache plugin &#8211; Cache Enabler<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-plugin-directory\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"suki-oembed\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"odhO3cg7HY\"><a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/cache-enabler\/\">Cache Enabler &#8211; WordPress Cache<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;Cache Enabler &#8211; WordPress Cache&#8221; &#8212; Plugin Directory\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/cache-enabler\/embed\/#?secret=odhO3cg7HY\" data-secret=\"odhO3cg7HY\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/webP-trong-Cache-Enabler.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"495\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/webP-trong-Cache-Enabler-1024x495.png\" alt=\"Webp Trong Cache Enabler\" class=\"wp-image-24152\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/webP-trong-Cache-Enabler-1024x495.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/webP-trong-Cache-Enabler-218x105.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/webP-trong-Cache-Enabler-300x145.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/webP-trong-Cache-Enabler-700x338.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/webP-trong-Cache-Enabler-768x371.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/webP-trong-Cache-Enabler.png 1630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>T\u00edch ch\u1ecdn \u00f4 webP trong Cache Enabler<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng plugin n\u00e0y v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111ang d\u00f9ng WP Rocket hay Hosting Cache.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>D\u00f9ng Cache Plugin &#8211; Litespeed Cache<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-plugin-directory\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"suki-oembed\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"JOx2gMkhCN\"><a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/litespeed-cache\/\">LiteSpeed Cache<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;LiteSpeed Cache&#8221; &#8212; Plugin Directory\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/litespeed-cache\/embed\/#?secret=JOx2gMkhCN\" data-secret=\"JOx2gMkhCN\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u00f9ng OpenLiteSpeed web server thay v\u00ec Apche hay Nginx server th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eadt webP trong server-side plugin Litespeed Cache nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/litespeed-cache-plugin.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"862\" height=\"565\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/litespeed-cache-plugin.png\" alt=\"Litespeed Cache Plugin\" class=\"wp-image-24179\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/litespeed-cache-plugin.png 862w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/litespeed-cache-plugin-218x143.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/litespeed-cache-plugin-300x197.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/litespeed-cache-plugin-700x459.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/litespeed-cache-plugin-768x503.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 862px) 100vw, 862px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>C\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh weP trong Litespeed Cache plugin<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>D\u00f9ng Shortpixel Image Optimizer Plugin<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-plugin-directory\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"suki-oembed\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"J03IRh7zbv\"><a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/shortpixel-image-optimiser\/\">ShortPixel Image Optimizer<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;ShortPixel Image Optimizer&#8221; &#8212; Plugin Directory\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/shortpixel-image-optimiser\/embed\/#?secret=J03IRh7zbv\" data-secret=\"J03IRh7zbv\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n v\u00e0o th\u1ebb Advanced c\u1ee7a Shortpixel \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/cach-dung-WebP-tren-shortpixel.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"390\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/cach-dung-WebP-tren-shortpixel-1024x390.png\" alt=\"Cach Dung Webp Tren Shortpixel\" class=\"wp-image-24150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/cach-dung-WebP-tren-shortpixel-1024x390.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/cach-dung-WebP-tren-shortpixel-218x83.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/cach-dung-WebP-tren-shortpixel-300x114.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/cach-dung-WebP-tren-shortpixel-700x267.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/cach-dung-WebP-tren-shortpixel-768x292.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/cach-dung-WebP-tren-shortpixel.png 1589w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng <code>.htaccess<\/code> ho\u1eb7c chuy\u1ec3n \u1ea3nh sang <code>&lt;Picture&gt;<\/code> tag \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng webP<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn 1 trong 2 c\u00e1ch tr\u00ean. N\u1ebfu web server b\u1ea1n \u0111ang l\u00e0 Nginx server th\u00ec b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch <code>.htaccess<\/code>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>D\u00f9ng Shortpixel CDN<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng Shortpixel b\u1eb1ng Autoptimize Plugin th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 sau<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/bat-webP-trong-autoptimize.png\"><im